{"title":"野营来到半屏山","authors":["曹树莹"],"dates":[{"year":1979,"month":8,"day":11}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"野营来到半屏山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"解放军某部战士  曹树莹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"野营来到半屏山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心头情思滚滚翻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"半屏山上风光好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有半屏在台湾。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫说一山分两半，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫说骨肉不团圆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海峡碧波似裙带，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山高水阔俩相连。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几十年分离长相思，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山山水水将你盼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都是一轮明月照，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为啥骨肉不团圆？！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"半屏山哪半屏山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国的呼声可听见？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"涛声变成丝竹日，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"且将海峡作琴弦……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}